Use the {{incode|viewIsometric}} method of the View object to change to isometric view. The {{incode|viewDimetric}} and {{incode|viewTrimetric}} methods are also available.

{{Code|code=
import FreeCADGui

view = FreeCADGui.ActiveDocument.ActiveView
view.viewIsometric()
}}


